Module org.apache.jena.arq
Package org.apache.jena.sparql.algebra.walker

Interface OpVisitorByType

All Superinterfaces:
OpVisitor
public interface OpVisitorByType extends OpVisitor
A visitor helper that maps all visits to a few general ones. Does not visit expressions at all.
